'''Anadyr''' ({{lang-ru|Ана́дырь}}) is a river in the far northeast Siberia which flows into [[Anadyr Bay]] of the [[Bering Sea]] and drains much of the interior of [[Chukotka Autonomous Okrug]]. Its basin corresponds to the [[Anadyrsky District]] of Chukotka.
